description: Simply say a phrase such as "give me a cat fact" or "tell me a fact" and this skill set will fulfill all your cat trivia wonders and needs.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask cat trivia to give me a cat fact
Alexa, ask cat trivia to tell me something
Alexa, ask cat trivia to give me some information
name: My Cat Facts
shortDescription: Ever find yourself wondering about cats? Curious to learn some interesting trivia? Looking to pass time? This is the skill set for you!
